        "input": "What happened with NVDA.US recently?",
        "output": [
          "A grouped digest with earnings, strategic, regulatory, analyst, filing, and community sections.",
          "Each item includes a date, one factual point, source labeling, and a neutral key takeaway.",
          "The answer ends with a clear note that it is not investment advice."
        ]
      },
      {
        "input": "Analyze the latest 8-K for a US-listed company.",
        "output": [
          "A filing summary with form type, filing date, event description, and likely market relevance.",
          "The analysis separates facts from bull, bear, and neutral interpretations."
        ]
      },
